How to drink cheap on a plane..
Pffft rookies. I have a bunch of little Scope bottles, fill with vodka add a drop of blueberry Mio. It changes errythang.
Seriously, adding Mio to vodka changed my life. Just a little, tiny bit, but it was a positive change nonetheless.
